      <title>Dollar Sprieve将全球资金带回新兴亚洲股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-23/dollar-reprieve-brings-global-funds-back-to-emerging-asia-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元的集会暂停和美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的最初关税遭到惩罚，投资者正在向亚洲新兴市场的股票升温，而不是较早设想的惩罚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-23/dollar-reprieve-brings-global-funds-back-to-emerging-asia-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Feb 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
