      <title>美联储的通货膨胀量表将简化至七个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-22/fed-favored-inflation-gauge-is-set-to-ease-to-seven-month-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储的首选通货膨胀指标预计将冷却至6月以来最慢的速度，但是驯服价格压力的冰川进展总体上将使决策者谨慎降低利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-22/fed-favored-inflation-gauge-is-set-to-ease-to-seven-month-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Feb 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
